text: Ðis is þara þreora hida landboc æt beorchamme þe Eadred cyning gebocode Ælfwine his þegene on ece yrfe.
Þis synd þara þreora hida londgemæro to Beorcham.

Ærest þæt of Ceollanwylle andlang riþe to yge to þæs hagan end þonne andlang hagan to Cnottinga hamme þonne of Cnottinga hamme forþ be wyrtwalan andlang slades to hwitan stane þonne from hwitan stane andlang stræt to Loddera stræt þonne of Loddera stræt eft to Ceollanwylle.
